sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as "Local browser/test client"
    participant Page as "BlogAI.Web /local-dev"
    participant UiService as "IBlogAiLocalAuthStatusService"
    participant Consumer as "IBlogAiAuthConsumerService"
    participant Auth as "AdventuresAuthDecisionService"
    participant Rendered as "Rendered protected placeholder and metadata"

    Client->>Page: GET /local-dev
    Page->>UiService: GetStatus()
    UiService->>Consumer: Evaluate protected placeholder without dev marker
    Consumer->>Auth: Validate local protected access
    Auth-->>Consumer: Denied decision with correlation metadata
    Consumer-->>UiService: Display-safe denied result
    UiService->>Consumer: Evaluate protected placeholder with internal dev marker
    Consumer->>Auth: Validate local protected access
    Auth-->>Consumer: Allowed decision with safe principal placeholder
    Consumer-->>UiService: Display-safe allowed result
    UiService-->>Page: Hidden and shown placeholder display model
    Page-->>Rendered: Hidden denied placeholder, shown allowed placeholder, CorrelationId, RequestId, AuthDecisionId
    Rendered-->>Client: 200 OK

    Note over Page,Rendered: Razor renders display-safe model only
    Note over UiService,Auth: Auth decision ownership remains in BlogAI auth consumer and AdventuresAuth services
    Note over Page,Rendered: Raw credential, token, secret, header, and password sentinels are not rendered
    Note over Page,Auth: No production deployment, OAuth/OpenID/RBAC, persistence/database, BlogEngine.NET coupling, or new auth middleware
